== Entrances & Exits ==
=== Entrances ===
* Walking into an area that is covered in orange fog within [[Level 660]] may transition the level into [[Level 677]].
* Rare doorways labeled “Maintenance Access” within the deeper regions of [[Level 655]] lead directly to the concrete expanse of [[Level 677]] when opened.
* No-clipping through a strangely positioned orange wall within the stairs of [[Level 168]] leads one to [[Level 677]].

=== Exits ===
* A rare and strange ventilation duct on the concrete ground can be found when explored enough and screwing out the grate, opens to [[Level 678]].
* Following the directions of rare road signs may direct to a road that transitions the level into [[Level 690]].
* After extended periods of time, No-clipping into the concrete ground may be possible and sends one to [[Level 798]].
</div>
